Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to stage an all-out\Nmissile attack on the colonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can't fight, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really no way out,\Nwith all this security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, to swipe a carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd have to cross the\Ndesert to get to an airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With all those planes\Nlooking for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're stuck, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A large sandstorm\Nis coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we'll cross\Nthe desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use some sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I need time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've collected what we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But the important parts\Nhave all been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he self-detonated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So even Gundams end up\Nas mere scraps of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, scraps of Gundanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This Gundam design was\Nbased on the Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the basic technology utilized\Nfor the Tallgeese should apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I took\Nthis Gundam with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the Lake Victoria Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'm preoccupied\Nwith that pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gundam pilot died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty well impossible\Nafter that explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As a fellow mobile suit pilot,\NI was destined to battle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have acted\Non my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...to plan a direct attack\Non the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's water under\Nthe bridge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know that the\NGundam attacks were planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...by certain people,\Nto retaliate against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our target is still to destroy\Nall of the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But their supporters concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to keep the enemy\Nfrom becoming more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I rely on you, Lady Une?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eliminate them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Your Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace-minded people\Nof the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't stand any militarism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do away with\Nsome of your formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Announce your trip to outer\Nspace when you're in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Many noble people who\Nunderstand OZ live in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be able\Nto assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing on the radar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't mean{\i0}\N{\i1}a damn thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread out and watch\Nfor enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I can't see a thing\Nin this sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a middle east{\i0}\N{\i1}nations' military base...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...unaffiliated with the United{\i0}\N{\i1}Earth Sphere Alliance or OZ.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take refuge there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A base?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problems here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An underground base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H- Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This base belongs to our{\i0}\N{\i1}Maganac Corps' homeland.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's your base?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good of you to come, Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while,\NCommander Sadaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The missions have been tough\Nsince you got to Earth, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe the Maganac Corps\Nfor all their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was their personal decision;\Nthey wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had more strength\Nwe could've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...more damage to OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That troublesome OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A sensible person wouldn't\Nuse the colonies as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're to blame, for not\Nstopping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're totally to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre, we'll get started\Nwith the mobile suit repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Rashid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll repair both Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Quatre Raberba Winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Winner family's heir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The influential and financial\Npower of the Arabic Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder everyone looks up\Nto you around this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family is all pacifists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I disinherited myself\Nto come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes all types, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Duo. Duo Maxwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I might run and hide,\Nbut I never tell a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were told that the colonies{\i0}\N{\i1}have sent mobile suits to Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true that a number of{\i0}\N{\i1}mobile suits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...were sent to Earth and tried{\i0}\N{\i1}to destroy certain targets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However OZ is currently taking{\i0}\N{\i1}steps to expose the rebels...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so it can maintain{\i0}\N{\i1}world peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's only a matter of time{\i0}\N{\i1}before we solve this issue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That rose doesn't suit\Nher one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't she cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, but this party\Nis open only to invited guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Katrina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know any\Nother guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Marquis Weridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry; I had\Nno idea she was your relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The party's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is full of old folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Young people like yourself\Nare a rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Mr. Weridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pretty young date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do. I'm Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have this dance miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The first dance is already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wouldn't mind,\Ncould I have this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I mind;\NI'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've guarded the{\i0}\N{\i1}front entrance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problems at the rear{\i0}\N{\i1}gate or along the channel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Radar picking up nothing{\i0}\N{\i1}in the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continue to post guard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the Peacecraft\Ninfluence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the Peacecrafts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was close to the Sanc Kingdom\Nmonarchy, the Peacecrafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Till 13 years ago, when\Nthe family was overthrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was the Peacecraft\Nfamily overthrown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems absurd, but while\Nsome people hope for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...others try to gain\Nthrough disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The former was the\NPeacecraft family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the latter was the\NUnited Earth Sphere Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their talk of peace interfered\Nwith the Alliance's objectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and even the Romefeller\NFoundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...which opposed the Alliance,\Nstarted developing weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasted OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited Treize today to ask\Nwhat he was trying to pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sent over some\Nrepresentative!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry; I'm a guest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me to Marquis Weridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I must see him personally,\Non behalf of His Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Roses don't belong on\Nmilitary uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A rose is more suitable for\Nsomeone kind like you, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Marquis Weridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I come on behalf of\NTreize Khushrenada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Lady Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, would you\Ngive me that rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give it to\Nmy granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena Darlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, roses don't\Nlook good on me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd look better soaked\Nin the blood of OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's for my dad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Marquis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing in your way is\Nabout the only thing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't match her courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all fans of that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take the main entrance!\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need her kind of courage\Nin order to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much for me to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're celebrating the return\Nof us 40 Maganac soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The nation opposes the Alliance\NMilitary and defends itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Maganac are the\Nfront-line troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more like heroes\Nthan front-line soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's completely united now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this nation's\Nso positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This nation is unified and is\Ngonna stick it out to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot I wanna\Ntalk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Quatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got questions, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's five, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the five of us that\Nmet at New Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here from the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The five of us are very\Nsimilar, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mobile suits and\Nour missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention our goal\Nto destroy OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ destroyed peace in\Nthe colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission is revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fighting under\Nthose orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I was given\Nthe mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Destroy them first."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's your responsibility."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always fought believing\NI'd be better off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...than live under OZ's rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But to kill yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero ended up doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He took his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies have no\Nintention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies can't be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend was the\Nperfect role model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've imagined\Nthat Heero was so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies were a clear target\Nonce the Gundams got going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle where the nation\Nisn't unified as one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more difficult\Nfor a lonely soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's mobile suit troops\Nare coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this, Rashid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like their reconnoiter\Ntroops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rashid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start fighting here,\Nthe civilians will get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then keep on guard but send\Nthe soldiers underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some nomadic friends stopped\Nby at the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let our troops rest\Nand share your food and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We hear middle east rebels\Nare hiding out in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here for precautionary\Npurposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Check those boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's set so any movement\Nwill trigger it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashid, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ played dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile they were setting\Ntwenty bombs across town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're time bombs we\Njust need to trash them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're designed so we\Ncan't move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They've narrowed our troops'\Nlocation down to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they're gonna\Nforce us to surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They've set the bombs to\Ngo off at 12 midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be hoping for\Na nighttime battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So OZ is preparing to battle\Nwith us overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they think we're gonna\Nsurrender before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't the Gundams causing\Nthis problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their attack is well planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They've probably been\Nwatching this town for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has discovered this town\Nand will be attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt if we'll be able to\Ndeceive them any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we'll aim at one\Narea of their besieging line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and resist while helping\Nthe civilians escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One other honorable\Nduty remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must get the two\NGundams out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams are heroes that\Narrived on Earth to destroy OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of OZ's scheming, the\NGundams can't fight this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will be a day when\Nthe Gundams will save us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Be thankful that you can return\Nthe favor in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hover suits from the middle{\i0}\N{\i1}east troops are attacking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tragos troops, fire!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy's hover suits{\i0}\N{\i1}are too quick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tragos Hover suits,{\i0}\N{\i1}shift to the back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Close combat's too dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragos ready to fire at enemy's\Nunderground exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that was\Nour only exit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By the North Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of enemy\Ncarriers to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't rush.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They haven't guarded{\i0}\N{\i1}the North Mountain Gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get separated from{\i0}\N{\i1}your families!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this to the North Gate,\Nwhere Abdul's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I can't do anything\Nin return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams are our heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we'll fight together\Nagain some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Quatre!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some flowers\Nhere for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One day my Gundam will\Ndefinitely fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Decoy operations are complete\Nand we're fleeing to the hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd blemish the Maganac\NCorps name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure a path for Master\NQuatre's carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maganac Corps, gather up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the enemy\Nthrough the barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quatre...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you circle the sky\Njust once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanna do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep firing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All Maganac Corps,\Nretreat at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again, Maganac Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, the colonies'\Nthoughts will be united.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl! Keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking care of her\Nfrom now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have special orders\Nfrom Colonel Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take orders from\Nyou, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These orders are from\NHis Excellency, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse our misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who your\Ntemperament takes after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of OZ right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Relena Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One must use weapons\Nto win back peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In a battlefield filled with\Ninconsistencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...Wu Fei meets Sally Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei states that the weaker\Nshould not be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But with those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally senses the complexity\Nof a cornered warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lost in his emotions, Wu Fei\Nreturns to his Shenlong Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bewildered Warriors".
